%h2 about playground society
%p
  Playground Society is a way to bring more play into your life.
%p
  The basic idea: You will get 2 or 3 text messages a week, each a simple Play Mission. The missions are designed to be fun, and meant to fit seamlessly into your normal day-to-day. 
%p
  As an extension of the play, you may also snap a picture of the mission and upload it to your profile. After you receive a mission, you have effectively unlocked it, and you can see everyone's documentation for that mission. 
%p
  Here are some sample 
  %a(href="/play")Play Missions.
